After returning to Rome, he obtained the quaestorship, the lowest senatorial office. As the minimum age for this was twenty- five,G he cannot have held it before 87. It seems most probable that his term was from July 1, 89, to June 30, 90. The fact that he was quaestor Caesaris indicates that he was in high favor with the emperor Domitian at this time.
